# Public, build-time-injected ID for Google Analytics (gtag.js).
# Optional — leave unset and the website ships without analytics.
#
# This value is exposed in the served HTML to every visitor (it's a public
# identifier, not a secret). It lives in env so:
#   - the production deploy uses your GA property,
#   - forks/local clones don't accidentally send analytics anywhere,
#   - preview deployments can opt out by leaving it unset.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=
